data.title: 2014 Prosperita Open
data.meta_description: The 2014 Prosperita Open was a professional tennis tournament played on clay courts. It was the eleventh edition of the tournament which was part of the 2014 ATP Challenger Tour. It took place in Ostrava, Czech Republic between 28 April and 4 May 2014.
